---
import HardSkills from '../components/HardSkills.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title='Rachhen'>
  <section class='px-4'>
    <div class='flex flex-col gap-4'>
      <p class='text-[16px] text-neutral-700'>
        I'm Rachhen, a software engineer from Siem Reap, Cambodia, is passionate
        about technology and specializes in Full-Stack development, Mobile App
        creation, and API development. With a commitment to continuous learning
        and a positive mindset, I'm approaches challenges with perseverance.
        Outside of work, I enjoys watching anime and reading Manga for
        relaxation and creativity. I aims to make meaningful contributions to
        the tech industry and is currently employed as a Full-Stack, Mobile App,
        and API developer. Eager to bring expertise and determination to new
        opportunities, I seeks to thrive in the dynamic world of technology and
        is open to discussing potential collaborations.
      </p>
    </div>
    <h2 class='mb-4 mt-7 text-3xl font-semibold'>Work Experience</h2>
    <div class='flex flex-col gap-7'>
      <div>
        <h3 class='mb-2 text-xl font-semibold'>Full-Stack Developer</h3>
        <h5 class='font-medium text-neutral-700'>
          <span class='rounded-md bg-primary px-2 text-xs text-white'
            >2018 - 2020</span
          >
          <span class='ml-2'>eOcambo Technology / Siem Reap</span>
        </h5>
        <p class='mt-3 text-[16px] font-normal text-neutral-700'>
          When I was developing a system for internal use. I got a lot of
          experience. We are using Yii2 Framework as tooling.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class='mb-2 text-xl font-semibold'>Mobile App with React Native</h3>
        <h5 class='font-medium text-neutral-700'>
          <span class='rounded-md bg-primary px-2 text-xs text-white'
            >2020 - Present</span
          >
          <span class='ml-2'> Prointix (Euro Khmer Voyages) / Siem Reap</span>
        </h5>
        <p class='mt-3 text-[16px] font-normal text-neutral-700'>
          I'm working on the mobile app with React Native. We are using
          TypeScript, React-Query, apollo client and zustand as state
          management. I have connected payment gateway with ABA.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class='mb-2 text-xl font-semibold'>Backend Developer</h3>
        <h5 class='font-medium text-neutral-700'>
          <span class='rounded-md bg-primary px-2 text-xs text-white'
            >2021 - Present</span
          >
          <span class='ml-2'> Prointix (Euro Khmer Voyages) / Siem Reap</span>
        </h5>
        <p class='mt-3 text-[16px] font-normal text-neutral-700'>
          I'm working on the backend of the system. We are using NestJs with
          RestAPI/GraphQL and MySQL as databases. the payment gateway is using
          ABA. And deploy the system to AWS or Fly.io services.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2 class='mb-4 mt-8 text-3xl font-semibold'>Education</h2>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4'>
      <div>
        <span class='rounded-md bg-primary px-2 text-xs text-white'
          >2016 - 2019</span
        >
        <h3 class='text-xl font-semibold'>Information technology</h3>
        <p class='text-sm font-normal text-neutral-700'>
          Build Bright University
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class='rounded-md bg-primary px-2 text-xs text-white'
          >2019 - 2020</span
        >
        <h3 class='text-xl font-semibold'>Mobile App with React Native</h3>
        <p class='text-sm font-normal text-neutral-700'>Self-taught</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class='rounded-md bg-primary px-2 text-xs text-white'
          >2020 - 2021</span
        >
        <h3 class='text-xl font-semibold'>Backend Developer</h3>
        <p class='text-sm font-normal text-neutral-700'>Self-taught</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <HardSkills />
    <h2 class='mt-8 text-3xl font-semibold'>Soft Skills</h2>
    <ul class='mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:w-[60%]'>
      <li>Fast Learning</li>
      <li>Creative Thinking</li>
      <li>Team work</li>
      <li>Empathy</li>
      <li>Problem Solving</li>
      <li>Communication</li>
      <li>Time Management</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
